	<p>After a pull that your pet manage's to survive but only due to him enraging.  Put your pet in his little pocket and then pull him right back out.  This will reset all his meele ability timers.<br />
<br />
The way mobs are facing also affects the distance they will assist as well.  If they have thier back to you they have much shorter agro range then one looking at you or the mob your pulling.</p>
	
	
	
