	<td class="alt1" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>One method/trick i didnt see mentioned is to pull with a low aggro spell, like malo/malos. My main is a ranger and the ranger community commonly uses jolt pulls to split up mobs, the assist radius seems to be affected by the hate generated when spell pulling.  After a nasty set of wipes in ldon i took over pulls on my shaman, useing root pulls, proximity and malo i rarely got more than 1-2. Just something a few of you may want to try.</p>
	
	
	
	
	
