</span></td>
	
	<td class="alt1" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>I just pulled Ruj a few times tonight. Ruj max mob scenario is like 3 IMO. So on those three id pull w/ slow, sic pet on add, vp other add and it was np. If the one add resisted VP i would slow it and offtank it. Never had to bust out the spirit call peel trick but it works wonders as described. I also have defensive AA's which help a lot. Get an extended range item. For me it is Clay Bracers of the Golem. This lets you MD/VP pull a lot safer. Another trick is if for somereason you have 3 unslowed mobs in camp Tigir's Insects is a good spell. It should be renamed Take One For The Team but if the group is good youll be healed and all will be well. Its not so much to slow 3 mobs at once, but to take aggro off the cleric. Also groups like chain pulling. I would pull a mob(with slow), sic pet, sinia it, Bane it and run off to grab another mob. Don't be oor when it dies or you wont get exp. Those are what I have learned so far, good luck!</p>
	
	
	
