	<td class="alt2" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>Just a lil note.<br />
<br />
Anathema is a GREAT investment for rooting and rotting.  Its a 278/tik curse DoT with NO DD.  i believe that it is 510 pts in Ruj LDoN....<br />
<br />
When you root/split mobs and intend to lend a DPS hand...DoTs with DDs on them are more likley to break root.  Epic-Ultor-Anathema-Blood of Saryn are the 4 best DoTs for root rotting CC'd mobs as they have NO DD on them. <br />
<br />
That is just based on my experience, dont mean for it to be about rooting and rotting, just mean that if you intend to root/split mobs and THEN DoT them, BECAREFUL, DD's on DoTs can break root and bring the mob running at you.<br />
<br />
<br />
Cascet Wurmhardt~65 shammy of the Nameless</p>
	
	
	
	
