	<td class="alt1" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>If a mob resists VP even after MD then try to run back to camp and root with normal root. I tend to pull with slow a lot because I can offtank a slowed mob NP. If you do happen to get one rooted Bane is actually the best DoT (420/tick over 30 seconds). Also to clear it up Anathema is bought for 410 points at the Butcherblock camp whereas Bane is bought for 650 points in the East Commonlands theme. Offtanking is more fun though, dunno why you'd rot.</p>
	
	
	
