	<p>Bear form allows you to see through walls.<br />
<br />
Shrinking twice and sitting also allows you to see through walls (Iksar with luclin models,  I hear no luclin models is better for this though).<br />
<br />
Also, casting Assiduous Vision on yourself is a good way to see around corners if you arent using the see-through-walls trick.  It also adds ultravision if you are a blind race (for you barbs out there) and it lasts forever.</p>
	
	
	
	
	
